/>"},{"pid":"48f2c91be5c454cb53f56fce836288445dc98e10","tid":293984,"uid":33788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:48:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次飲都會屙，岩岩飲左一杯就屙到仆街<br />\n屙水果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">好似用屎眼屙尿咁</span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁有冇扯旗同想比人屌屎眼</span></blockquote><br />\n咁又無</blockquote><br />\n屌你癡撚線嫁咩"},{"pid":"9ebe1ec66d14922e0a2bbfa00faa5dc3340885d6","tid":293984,"uid":73004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T02:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲盒裝要雪個啲奶屙到仆街<br />\n飲開之前唔洗雪個啲奶冇事<br />\n有冇人一樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你望下兩盒奶成分一唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有d係溝出黎"},{"pid":"b096c9a85df39dace9bbff19e799782dca119cd6","tid":293984,"uid":72587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:07:25.000Z","msg":"好似話係正常<br />\n人大左身體就會覺得唔需要再飲奶<br />\n所以會乳糖不耐<br />\n好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e35176f7408883625f488b056b37bff00a26e6f","tid":293984,"uid":26090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T03:50:49.000Z","msg":"飲奶冇事,飲朱奶,屙到菊花盛開<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5408a91ec1c38a2fe72fa641b9cfa6bf869d98a","tid":293984,"uid":61712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"食辣飲奶會嘔到仆街 加發燒"},{"pid":"72b843df4551e2e5eda3f1a28b7292bf88537d4f","tid":293984,"uid":1690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:14:23.000Z","msg":"飲奶後個肚會攪下攪下 咕咕聲<br />\n食乳酪芝士果啲仲會放足幾日無聲極臭屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似消化不良咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ac67a549