jDLDDMX5U%2B3TANqbjGCQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9a455b8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.iherb.com/pr/Natural-Factors-Lactase-Enzyme-9000-FCC-ALU-60-Capsules/2596</a>"},{"pid":"433ca660d9fa7edbb7ad33308daee50947db1670","tid":293984,"uid":1208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T07:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啱啱睇到篇文章話<br />\n原來某啲奶製品會加入乳糖酶<br />\n因為人啲腸入面有乳糖酶就可以幫助消化乳糖<br />\n所以有人飲A奶會屙 飲B奶就唔會？<br />\n<br />\n跟住睇到原來有乳糖酶既supplement賣<br />\n食奶製品果陣啪一粒 就唔會屙<br />\n出街都可以瘋狂飲奶同食雪糕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.iherb.com/pr/Natural-Factors-Lactase-Enzyme-9000-FCC-ALU-60-Capsules/2596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.iherb.com%2Fpr%2FNatural-Factors-Lactase-Enzyme-9000-FCC-ALU-60-Capsules%2F2596&d=EUjDLDDMX5U%2B3TANqbjGCQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=9a455b8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.iherb.com/pr/Natural-Factors-Lactase-Enzyme-9000-FCC-ALU-60-Capsules/2596</a></blockquote><br />\n正喎，屌你好似啪避孕丸咁"}]}